{"id":573297,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/午夜美术馆｜高氏兄弟：夜访大兴新建村记/","date":"2017-11-29T02:25:22Z","modified":"2017-11-29T03:06:23Z","title":"午夜美术馆｜高氏兄弟：夜访大兴新建村记","content":"<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573299\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/640-25.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"418\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/640-25.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/640-25-300x228.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>昨日下午近三时，友人孟煌君来电相约同走大兴新建村，并言明去之理由：为己言说获得合法性。其言甚合我意，当即邀来东启小弟三人共聚同行。由798出门，乘出租车至将台路转乘14号线至南站，继转6号线至西红门，出地铁乘滴滴直奔新建村，其时天色已黑。途中余拍照不慎闪光，司机大怒曰：“执法钓鱼吧，下车！”吾等急忙解释说明去向缘由方使其息怒；一路，其怒斥恶警欺人世道无良，并嘱吾等进村若遇不测如何脱身，由此可见天赋良知存于人心，是非正邪尽人皆知，无需非得文人教诲启蒙而后方明事理。至目的地，吾等下车巡视，村内灯暗路黑满目萧然：废墟触目，弃物杂陈，垃圾遍地，偶见零星撤离者搬运余物，或三五村民立于巷口，抑或警查保安若干巡视游荡或排立于村内头，一派失地沦陷景观。吾等随走随拍，并与所见者攀谈，被驱者声泪俱下，称当年日寇亦非如今日当局这般专横；原住民唉声叹气曰百姓何奈；警保则三缄其口默不作声。吾等走街窜巷，现场尽睹驱离地破败景象，感觉如入塔利班、巴尔干战后地带废墟巡游，或疑心梦入好莱坞灾难片影棚探班。此国俨然早已超级噩梦工厂化，想必好莱坞编剧之想象亦难企及梦国出品之现实灾难片之奇特魔幻之境界。考察两小时余，吾等走出新建村，搭滴滴、乘地铁返程，寻一夜店觅食，而后各自归家，是时已入三更。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573303\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/640-26-213x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"775\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/640-26-213x300.jpg 213w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/640-26.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573307\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/1-4-300x227.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"416\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/1-4-300x227.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/1-4.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573309\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/2-2-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/2-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/2-2.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573311\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/3-3-300x229.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/3-3-300x229.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/3-3.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573312\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/4-2-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/4-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/4-2.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573313\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/5-2-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/5-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/5-2.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573314\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/6-1-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/6-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/6-1.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573315\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/7-1-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/7-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/11/7-1.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-5733